Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}コイ感情かな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}迷い道依って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}距離感を知って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}今の私は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:46.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}恋を　色を　夢も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:47.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(100,100)}全部
